import "./order.css"; import Header from "../Components/Header/Header"; import Title from '../Components/Title/Title' import SummaryTable from './Components/Summary_table/table' import DetailTable from './Components/Detail_table/table' function Order(props) { return (
<div className="order-content"> <div className="order-detail"> <h2>Order Details</h2> <DetailTable /> </div> <div className="order-summary"> <h2>Order Summary</h2> <SummaryTable /> </div> <form action="" id="myfeedback"> <label for="myfeedback">Firstname:</label> <input type="text" id="fname" name="fname"/> <input type="submit"/> </form> </div> </div> ); } export default Order;
